2.Eventhough the website is not needed to scalae up but I have coded in way that is future proof by utilising CSS variables.
3.This website is developed in a way that the maintanance and refactoring of this website is made easy.
4.Website is a responsive for both mobile and for the desktop by leveraging the flexibility of the media queries in CSS.
